### Get all orders for a user
GET http://localhost:3000/user/johndoe/order

### Get a specific order by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/user/johndoe/order/60d7c319f1a5c1532c90b84e

### Create a new order for a user
POST http://localhost:3000/user/johndoe/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderDate": "2024-07-01",
  "groceryItems": [
    { "name": "Apples", "quantity": 5 },
    { "name": "Bananas", "quantity": 7 }
  ]
}

### Update a specific grocery item in an order
PUT http://localhost:3000/user/johndoe/order/grocery/60d7c319f1a5c1532c90b84e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oranges",
  "quantity": 10
}

### Delete a specific grocery item from an order
DELETE http://localhost:3000/user/johndoe/order/grocery/60d7c319f1a5c1532c90b84e